
FinnWordNet - the Finnish WordNet
=================================


FinnWordNet
-----------

FinnWordNet is a wordnet for Finnish. For more information about
FinnWordNet, please see the README file in the parent directory or

    http://urn.fi/urn:nbn:fi:lb-2014052714

The rest of this README file describes the contents of this directory.


lex: FinnWordNet in the Princeton WordNet lexicographer file format
-------------------------------------------------------------------

The directory 'lex' contains FinnWordNet data in the Princeton WordNet
(PWN) lexicographer file format, which is the source format for the
PWN database:

    http://wordnet.princeton.edu/wordnet/man/wninput.5WN.html

The FinnWordNet lexicographer files correspond exactly to the PWN
ones.

A modified version of the PWN Grind program generating the database is
required for the FinnWordNet lexicographer files.


Bugs
----

* Finnish verbs have a dummy verb frame (number 1) in order for the
  data to work with the 'wn' search tool.
